Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要花相当多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓个能通过警戒的人会更快些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像只披着羊皮的狼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托利
