Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机器鸟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那个人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 会飞哪去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯...兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢...谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从前的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最要好的朋友送的最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
